ment; suffix still triggers \"shorter wins\" dedup against the join\n- **Case 2:** \"SAFFRON WHEAT BUNS...\" - OCR character substitution issue (`:` vs `/`) plus fixed-value penalty insufficient for some embedding scores\n\n### 4. `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/5-218113e/feedback.md`\n\nThree failures from iteration 5:\n\n- **Case 1:** \"Baked Eggs...\" - split title destroyed by dedup's \"shorter wins\" rule\n- **Case 2:** \"FINNISH MILK FLATBREADS...\" - structural bonus on first title inflates threshold, excluding second title\n- **Case 3:** \"SAFFRON WHEAT BUNS...\" - garbled OCR fragment passes structural heading check and hijacks the role\n\n### Committed Folder\n\nThe `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/7-9a83c46/committed` file contains a single line: `b5177f1` (the commit hash for iteration 7)."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aae9dcab46edf5011 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 74683\ntool_uses: 6\nduration_ms: 14909</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7bdf839d-85df-40e4-96e0-3a9dda0250b7","uuid":"6b0e9399-73a7-4196-97d8-8911e9a83e76","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these files and provide their full contents:\n1. /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/7-9a83c46/feedback.md (if exists)\n2. /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/7-9a83c46/improvement-plan.md (if exists)\n3. /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/6-8a6c985/feedback.md (if exists)\n4. /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/5-218113e/feedback.md (if exists)\n\nAlso check if there's a committed/ folder inside 7-9a83c46/ and list what's in it.","agentId":"aae9dcab46edf5011","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. Here are the files I found:\n\n## Files Retrieved\n\n### 1. `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/7-9a83c46/feedback.md`\n\nThis contains a 